ancestralarchetypes.archetype.descriptio: Water-loving Archetypes that thrive in the sea, but can dry out.
Mounted Archetypes that use a soulbound mount to get around.
Feline Archetypes that only eat meat and always land of their feet.
Slime-like Archetypes that dodge death. They bounce and are always hungry.
These Archetypes eat their material to heal and cannot regen naturally.
Fire-immune Archetypes that channel the Nether, but hate the cold.
Swampy Archetypes that are empowered by the moon and immune to poison.
Airy Archetypes that fall safely from heights and channel the wind.
